item.title: [HIVE-20593] Load Data for partitioned ACID tables fails with bucketId out of range: -1
item.description:
Load data for ACID tables is failing to load ORC files when it is converted to IAS job.

 

The tempTblObj is inherited from target table. However, the only table property which needs to be inherited is bucketing version. Properties like transactional etc should be ignored.
item.summary: Load Data for partitioned ACID tables fails with bucketId out of range: -1

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
